quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  100,10,aur jo ( bhaid ) dilon mein hain woh zahir kar diye jayen ge
  100,11,be shak un ka perwar-digaar is roz un se khoob waaqif hoga
  101,1,khar kharanay wali
  101,2,khar kharanay walikiya hai ?
  101,3,aur tumkiya jaanun khar kharanay walikiya hai ?
  101,4,( woh qayamat hai ) jis din log aisay hon ge jaisay bikhare hue patangay
  101,5,aur pahar aisay ho jayen ge jaisay dhanki hui rang barang ki oon
  101,6,to jis ke ( aamaal ke ) wazan bhaari nikleen ge
  101,7,woh dil pasand aish mein ho ga
  101,8,aur jis ke wazan halkay nikleen ge
  101,9,is ka marja hawiya hai
  101,10,aur tumkiya samjhay ke hawiyakiya cheez hai ?
  101,11,dehakti hui aag hai
  102,1,( logo ) tum ko ( maal ki ) bohat si talab ne ghaafil kar diya
  102,2,yahan taq ke tum ne qabrain ja dekhen
  102,3,dekho tumhe anqareeb maloom ho jaye ga
  102,4,phir dekho tumhe anqareeb maloom ho jaye ga
  102,5,dekho agar tum jantay ( yani ) ilm al-yaqeen ( rakhtay to ghaflat nah karte )
  102,6,tum zaroor dozakh ko dekho ge
  102,7,phir is ko ( aisa ) dekho ge ( ke ) ain al-yaqeen ( aa jaye ga )
  102,8,phir is roz tum se ( shukar ) Nemat ke baray mein prssh ho gi
